BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Outdoor Flow Yogis
UID:event_313874607@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260409T025721Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260409T181500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260409T190000
SUMMARY:movewell at weaver street market
DESCRIPTION:Outdoor Flow Yogis\nJoin Erica at [Weaver Street Market](https
 ://www.weaverstreetmarket.coop/location/raleigh/) for donation-based\, ope
 n level yoga and mat pilates classes from 6:15-7pm on select Thursdays in 
 March. Expand your movement practice and uplift our local community. Self-
 care never felt so good!\n\n2nd Thursday - **45min YOGA FLOW + CHILL** int
 egrates breathwork\, flowing waves of movement\, and a restorative cool do
 wn for a full body flow and wind-down\n\n4th Thursday - **45min PILATES MA
 T FLOW** combines core-focused matwork from Joseph Pilates' original mat s
 equence to strengthen your powerhouse\n\nClasses take place upstairs in th
 e Weaver Street Market event space. Street parking is free after 6pm - bri
 ng your own mat and a water bottle.\n\n**Sliding scale pricing to pay-what
 -u-can via cash\, venmo\, or paypal.** *NOTE - 50% of the proceeds from ea
 ch class will be donated to local organizations providing nutrition assist
 ance to those in need.*
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/outdoorflowyogis/events/313874607/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260320T231751Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260320T231751Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Outdoor Flow Yogis
UID:event_313912397@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260409T025721Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260412T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260412T120000
SUMMARY:Sunday Yoga at Trophy
DESCRIPTION:Outdoor Flow Yogis\n**S﻿unday Yoga** classes take place mont
 hly at [Trophy Brewing](https://www.trophybrewing.com/brewery-taproom)'s M
 aywood location. Join us inside the brewery or out on the lawn for a 60-mi
 nute yoga flow for all experience levels. Beginners welcome! Bring your ma
 t and any props you like to use.\n\nRegistration includes one drink ticket
 \, so stick around after class to enjoy a Trophy pint or non-alcoholic bev
 erage and relax with the crew—great way to start your Sunday FUNday.\n\n
 Cost: $22 cash/venmo at the door or reserve online [here](https://trophysu
 ndayyoga2026.eventbrite.com/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/outdoorflowyogis/events/313912397/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260323T160907Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260323T160907Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
